Pero Privacy Policy

Effective Date: 14 Feb 2024

Welcome to Pero! This Privacy Policy outlines how Pero ("we," "us," or "our") collects, uses, and protects your information when you use our app. By using Pero, you agree to the terms of this Privacy Policy.

1. Information We Collect:

User Account Information: To provide our services, we collect basic account information such as username and email address.

Location Data: When using live tracking features, Pero may collect and process location data to enable real-time location sharing within the app.

Drawing and Chat Data: We collect data related to live drawing and chatting activities within the app to facilitate real-time collaboration.

2. How We Use Your Information:

Service Provision: We use your information to provide live tracking, drawing, and chatting features, enhancing real-time collaboration experiences.

Communication: Your contact information may be used for communication purposes, such as app updates, notifications, or responding to inquiries.

Analytics: We may use anonymized and aggregated data for analytical purposes to improve Pero's features and performance.

3. Data Sharing:

Collaborative Features: Your live tracking, drawing, and chatting data are shared within the virtual room to enable collaborative experiences among users.

Third-Party Services: Pero is not integrate with any third-party services for enhanced functionality. Please review the privacy policies of these services for more information.

4. Security:

Data Security: We employ industry-standard security measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, disclosure, or alteration.
5. Your Choices:

Account Control: You can review, modify, or delete your account information within the app.

Location Sharing: Live tracking is a voluntary feature. You can control and disable location sharing within the app settings.

6. Updates to this Policy:

Policy Changes: We may update this Privacy Policy to reflect changes in our practices. Check the effective date for the latest version.
7. Contact Us:

If you have questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us at santosh95.freelance@gmail.com

Thank you for choosing Pero!
